<br>
On the other hand, if someone is nice and works well with the group...  chances are they're in it for the fun.  And if not, they managed to pull off an extra trance stick.  Big deal, I can't use it.  And selling isn't very much fun. = )<br>
<br>
If someone really wants to get something sold it goes up on the message board...and voila...there's your monk selling the extra trance stick.  Call him on it and don't group with him anymore. = )<br>
<br>
Just my opinion though.<br>
