<br>
Time for my : In my old guild speach.<br>
Raids :<br>
We had list for each class, as soon as you made 46 you got added to the bottom of the list. If you where at the top of the list you could choose to loot or not to loot an item. If you looted it all of your characters move to the bottom of there lists. If you didn't the next person down got the choice. Each raid you missed bumped you down a slot on the lists, more that 4 you where removed from them until you decided to start showing up to raids again, and then you got added to the bottom of the list.<br>
<br>
(and alot of bylaws but who cares about those)<br>
<br>
Groups :<br>
